snippet.title: Kill it With Fire - Launch Trailer [Spider Extermination Game]
snippet.description:
A terrible, terrible day for Spiders Worldwide. Get it on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179210/Kill_It_With_Fire/ 

Epic Games Store: https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/kill-it-with-fire/

#KillItWithFire #Spiders #arachnophobia

Kill It With Fire is a game about exterminating spiders by any means. That includes burning your house down.
